6
00:00:14.030 --> 00:00:17.810
Every stage leaks. Generators omit complex material classes.

7
00:00:17.810 --> 00:00:20.050
Universal machine-learned potentials are least reliable at surfaces,

8
00:00:20.050 --> 00:00:23.890
