16
00:00:38.540 --> 00:00:40.240
The field is fixed by three standard observables.

17
00:00:40.640 --> 00:00:41.700
A fourth surface is held back as a

18
00:00:41.700 --> 00:00:44.720
blind test. Across 36 model-and-material combinations, predicted and

19
00:00:44.720 --> 00:00:47.280
measured errors correlate at zero point nine oh

20
00:00:47.540 --> 00:00:48.880
six—with zero adjustable parameters.

21
00:00:49.380 --> 00:00:50.840
Quantitative claims are then sealed as Lean 4

22
00:00:50.840 --> 00:00:52.480
theorems with hash-locked provenance.

23
00:00:53.270 --> 00:00:55.170
The proof layer has 190 build-locked theorems and

24
00:00:55.170 --> 00:00:57.530
zero unfinished proofs. It once rejected a rounded

25
00:00:57.530 --> 00:01:00.290
success count, changing 27 improvements to 26.

26
00:01:00.630 --> 00:01:01.810
Trust means being able to say no to

27
00:01:01.810 --> 00:01:02.450
