33
00:01:14.550 --> 00:01:16.610
Users keep their simulators.

34
00:01:16.670 --> 00:01:17.810
Lupine makes them more trustworthy.

35
00:01:18.350 --> 00:01:20.510
Better materials infrastructure is estimated to create 123

36
00:01:20.510 --> 00:01:23.410
